creator: Maria Thompson Daviess
description:
LibriVox recording of The Heart's Kingdom (version 2 dramatic reading) by Maria Thompson Daviess.

Read in English by LibriVox volunteers.

Charlotte Powers is a woman who loves life, and is set to marry Nickols just as soon as she can figure herself out. However, coming home and meeting the charismatic pastor that seems to have influenced all her friends, tips her worldview, and she doesn't know what to do. Summary by Kristingj
